title: Boxing Match for Charity: Durianrider vs. À-Bas-Le-Ciel?
description:
Want to know more about the (vegan) storybook I'm proposing we'd raise donations for in the fundraiser?  Here's the link: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLZEkgohG7k7pperokk75ic6XpyLqy7MUw
Durianrider and I are both in Chiang Mai this Christmas: will there (finally) be a boxing match for charity in one of the town's arenas?  He's made threats of street-violence before (see the link, below, if you don't know how serious that situation once was), and I've responded by offering to meet him in the ring… repeatedly.
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLZEkgohG7k7rnlpe1mrR7bnaQwSaBYfij
Quoting myself from the fourth video in the playlist:
@22:45 "What more can I do for an audience of vegans who say they're trying to save the world, but who have gradually become accustomed to this culture of constant defamation and conspiratorial thinking?" 
​​@22:39 "We need to replace a culture of conspiracy-theory thinking with a culture of sincere engagement."
